General Assembly House Resolution No. 8
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 3058
Referred to Committee on Executive and Legislative Nominations
Introduced by:
REP. CONCEPCION, 4th Dist.
RESOLUTION CONFIRMING THE NOMINATION OF ELENA
TRUEWORTHY OF MANSFIELD TO BE COMMISSIONER OF EARLY
CHILDHOOD.
Resolved by this House:
1 That the nomination by His Excellency, the Governor, of Elena
2 Trueworthy of Mansfield, to be appointed Commissioner of Early
3 Childhood, to serve at the pleasure of the Governor, but not longer than
4 March 1, 2027, is hereby approved and confirmed.
